thread.title: BRIEF-Temasek Holdings (Private) Ltd Cuts Share Stake In JPMorgan Chase, Dissolves Share Stake in Athene Holding

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Temasek Holdings (Private) Ltd Cuts Share Stake In JPMorgan Chase, Dissolves Share Stake in Athene Holding
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Temasek Holdings (Private) Ltd :
* TEMASEK HOLDINGS (PRIVATE) LTD CUTS SHARE STAKE IN JPMORGAN CHASE & CO BY 33.3 PERCENT TO 176,225 SHARES
* TEMASEK HOLDINGS (PRIVATE) LTD UPS SHARE STAKE IN VISA INC BY 11.2 PERCENT TO 3.7 MILLION CLASS A SHARES - SEC FILING
* TEMASEK HOLDINGS (PRIVATE) LTD DISSOLVES SHARE STAKE IN ATHENE HOLDING LTD
* TEMASEK HOLDINGS (PRIVATE) LTD - CHANGE IN HOLDINGS ARE AS OF DEC 31, 2017 AND COMPARED WITH THE PREVIOUS QUARTER ENDED AS OF SEPT 30, 2017 Source text for quarter ended Dec 31, 2017: ( bit.ly/2EpcSgh ) Source text for quarter ended Sept 30, 2017: ( bit.ly/2yBi2ic )
